### Implied Naming Components

{%- if account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Environment-based)' %}
Based on your **Environment-based** account strategy:
- **Environment**: Implied by account name (`{{ target_account_name | upper }}`)
- **Domain**: Must be specified in object names
- **Data Product**: Must be specified in object names

Object names will follow the pattern: `<domain>_<dataproduct>_<zone>`
{%- elif account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Domain-based)' %}
Based on your **Domain-based** account strategy:
- **Domain**: Implied by account name (`{{ target_account_name | upper }}`)
- **Environment**: Must be specified in object names
- **Data Product**: Must be specified in object names

Object names will follow the pattern: `<dataproduct>_<zone>_<env>`
{%- elif account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Domain + Environment)' %}
Based on your **Domain + Environment** account strategy:
- **Domain**: Implied by account name (first component)
- **Environment**: Implied by account name (second component)
- **Data Product**: Must be specified in object names

Object names will follow the pattern: `<dataproduct>_<zone>`
{%- endif %}

### Connection Information

To execute SQL in subsequent steps, connect to:
- **Account**: `{{ target_account_name | upper }}`
- **Required Role**: SYSADMIN (for object creation)
- **Connection URL**: `https://<org>-{{ target_account_name | lower }}.snowflakecomputing.com`

> **Important:** Ensure you have SYSADMIN access to this account before proceeding.
